        {% elseif _tag.name == "Funchal" %}
          The latest news from Funchal. From local government to city events, stay informed about everything happening in the heart of Madeira.
        {% elseif _tag.name == "traffic" %}
          Stay informed on traffic, accidents, and transport related news that affect mobility.
        {% elseif _tag.name == "Airport" %}
          Breaking news from Cristiano Ronaldo International Airport. Track flight updates, airport infrastructure news, and travel alerts for Madeira.
        {% elseif _tag.name == "Rescue" %}
          Updates on search and rescue missions in Madeira. News from civil protection, mountain rescues, and emergency services.
        {% elseif _tag.name == "Nature" %}
          Explore Madeira’s natural beauty. News on the Laurissilva forest, levadas, environmental conservation, and local biodiversity.
        {% elseif _tag.name == "Tourism" %}
          Insights on the sector that drives Madeira. Latest news on tourism-related infos, travel statistics, and attractions for travelers.
